description:
This game is a not so well known epic gem. If you're into games like Crash Bandicoot, &amp; Ratchet &amp; Clank etc; then you'll love this very diverse neat little game that emulates easy, &amp; very well.

INFO:

As Kao, a brave kangaroo straight out of Australia, players are challenged to save the world of animals from an evil hunter and his wicked henchmen. With over 30 challenging enemies to overcome, Kao players are equipped with an array of fighting techniques from boomerang throwing to devastating tail attacks. Based on Kao the Kangaroo Round 2, the PSP-exclusive Kao Challengers features an action-packed single player mode.



System Requirements:

Core 2 duo 2.4GHz or higher.

nVidia GeForce GT 620 / ATI Radeon HD 5 series or higher.

3 Gig of ram or more.

Windows XP / Vista / 7 / 8 32 or 64bit OS.


